					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Rice krispy treats flavored with Jello</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody">years ago in High school or Junior High, a friend of mine made pink crispy treats and i remember she mentioned something about using Jello to color and flavor them.  I am looking for this recipe please.  I am DYING to make these.  Please help!!!</div>
