I made them yesterday from a box of cereal bought the same day and the recipe called for 3 Tbsp. butter, yet most online versions call for 4 Tbsp.  They seemed to get real hard, real fast, so I'm assuming the reduced butter contributes to it.  Microwaving for about 30 seconds on half power made them instantly soft again.<br />
